275 Triadimenol (1RS,2RS;1RS,2SR)-1-(4-chlorophenoxy)-3,3-dimethyl-1-(1H-1,2,4-triazol-1-yl)butan-2-ol ≥ 920 g/kg 1 September 2009 31 August 2019 PART A
